[]: &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Quote Post by robersora &raquo; Thu Oct 23, 2014 10:41 am Awesome, I always wondered, what was flashing there, but I never got around looking it up. Thank you very much! I especially like: Disregard of Common Sense. This sentence embodies the problem of communication which is a pretty big theme of the series very well, IMHO.

